    eyebrow: "AI tooling · PII scrubbing nodes",
    title: "Remove unnecessary identity before the model receives it.",
    lead: "PII scrubbing nodes are controlled points in an AI data path where sensitive information is classified, minimized, transformed, blocked, or routed for review. The objective is not indiscriminate redaction. It is to preserve the information a bounded task requires while reducing avoidable exposure.",
